200X-XX-XX  Lopatin Alexander  <sbar.geek@gmail.com>
    version 0.0.X
    selectable and editable QLabels are now having ibeam mouse cursor
    «system colors everywhere» is disabled by default
    tooltip in the character table now shows UTF-8 code and «value» is renamed to Unicode
    categories strings in qchardialog.cpp are moved to CharTable's QMap property instead of switch/case
    bold and italic buttons are affecting font info tab now
    CharsTable's scrolling bug fixed
    file can be opened via drug'n'drop
    added XML decimal entities in the CharsTable

